  <eligibility>
    <criteria>
      <textblock>
        Inclusion Criteria:

          -  Patients with class I or II pacing indications for Sick Sinus Syndrome with suspected
             paroxysmal atrial tachyarrhythmias over the last 6 months

          -  Signed informed consent

          -  Age &gt;18 yrs

        Exclusion Criteria:

          -  Severe valvular heart disease (echocardiogram less than 6 months old)

          -  Angina Pectoris class ≥ III

          -  Congestive heart failure - NYHA class ≥ III

          -  Left Ventricular Ejection Fraction &lt; 35% (less than 6 months old)

          -  Hypertrophic Cardiomyopathy
      </textblock>
    </criteria>
